text.tspan: Modern Web App
HTML5 + CSS3 + JavaScript
The standard ingredients for a modern
Web Application.
Styling & Responsive
Bootstrap + jQuery
Bootstrap is the elegant, responsive, mobile first
frame work with great styling. jQuery is a
requirement of Bootstrap. In other words: Make
V²Configurator look good and work on mobile,
tablet and the big screen.
Dynamic Views
Angular
V²Configurator is a highly dynamic single page web
app. You can fold / unfold content or load configur-
ations which modify a hundred objects, all without
contacting the server. Angular is the client-
side frame work to build clean web apps using the
Model-View-Controller Design pattern with clean
abstraction of view, data and logic.
Data (Store & Transport)
JSON + AJAX
JSON is short for JavaScript Object Notation. We use
this data format to store Configurator Data in files
on the Server and then to send this data to the
Client via AJAX.
